name: Frostfang Celestial Leviathan
text: Ascended from Frostfang, the Leviathan unfurled its quartet of wings, each a tapestry of cosmic ice. It roared, a sound like thunder, asserting its dominion over the tundra. Where Frostfang once guarded silently, this creature blazed with auroral fire, a sentinel in the eternal twilight, fierce and unyielding.

data.revised_prompt: Generate a digital artwork of an evolved, fantastical creature that merges qualities of a wolf and a dragon. This imposing figure sports two sets of majestic wings encrusted with ice, covered in iridescent scales that radiate a spectrum of colors against the backdrop of a twilight sky.
